metadata.name: Mistress of the Forest
metadata.description:
A pair of lovers wandered through the forest without keeping track of time. 

They would have continued their walk further, but unexpectedly for them, at sunset, they found themselves at the lake, which was the center of this forest.

In front of them appeared the silhouette of a woman who detachedly peered at the withered daffodil in her hand.

Soon a strange woman drew attention to the lovers, but what happened next remains a mystery...
